title: CIA Factbook Details on Countries
description:
Description
Country-level statistics from the US Central Intelligence Agency (CIA).

parameters.area: Land area, in square kilometers. (1 square kilometer is 0.386 square miles
parameters.death_rate: Death rate, in deaths per 1,000 people.
parameters.birth_rate: Birth rate, in births per 1,000 people.
parameters.infant_mortality_rate: Infant mortality, in deaths per 1,000 live births.
parameters.maternal_mortality_rate: Number of female deaths per 100,000 live births where the death is related to pregnancy or birth.
parameters.life_exp_at_birth: Live expectancy at birth, in years.

format: A data frame with 259 observations on the following 11 variables.
